symbols.name: KMap.extends
symbols.description: Inherit the prototype methods from one constructor into another.Usage:    function ParentClass(a, b) { }    ParentClass.prototype.foo = function(a) { }    function ChildClass(a, b, c) {      // Call parent constructor      ParentClass.call(this, a, b);    }    ol.inherits(ChildClass, ParentClass);    var child = new ChildClass('a', 'b', 'see');    child.foo(); // This works.
